title: [LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan SP 710-711 - Everybody Saw
description:
[LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan Special - 710-711 - Everybody Saw

Based on Files 831-833 of the Detective Conan manga by Gosho Aoyama. 

Bang. A body falls in an elevator. Right in front of everybody, a life is lost. Three suspects, one culprit. Heiji and Conan bring to light the story behind the apparent suicide. Just what happened? The first exclusive two-part special by LucarioPK. Everybody Saw.

Check back every Saturday in October for the next big case -- Hattori Heiji and the Vampire Mansion. It's the Halloween season, after all...
